{"tid":95073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷舊復古風潮加持，卡式錄音帶在美銷量成長 74 ％","createTime":"2017-01-25T17:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T16:46:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b98cda3722a7f1ebd4d512b60712c0095417eed2","tid":95073,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25175127/2017-01-24_162238-624x374.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F25175127%2F2017-01-24_162238-624x374.png&h=683dce4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在數位與串流音樂盛行的時代，原本已經逐漸式微的傳統卡式錄音帶（cassette），近年因音樂市場興起懷舊風潮而帶動了買氣，使銷量逐漸回溫成長。2016 年美國錄音帶總銷量為 12.9 萬卷，較前一年成長 74 ％，其具有「溫度」的魅力特質至今仍受到許多人喜愛。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25175409/2017-01-24_181922.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F25175409%2F2017-01-24_181922.png&h=03b05281&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國《告示牌》（Billboard）報導分析，2016 年錄音帶銷量主要來自多張西洋流行樂專輯，其中銷量最高的是漫威電影《星際異攻隊》原聲帶《勁爆舞曲大帝國》（Guardians of the Galaxy: Awesome Mix Vol. 1），連續兩年各以 4,000 卷銷量拿下錄音帶專輯銷售冠軍。 <br />\n<br />\n其他銷售破千卷的錄音帶專輯，還包括已故傳奇歌手王子（Prince）與樂團 The Revolution 專輯《紫雨》（Purple Rain）、饒舌歌手阿姆（Eminem）重發專輯《微暈》（The Slim Shady LP）、小賈斯汀（Justin Bieber）專輯《我的決心》（Purpose）、R&amp;B 歌手威肯（The Weeknd）專輯《狂野之美》（Beauty Behind the Madness）等等。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，2016 年 10 月 8 日所舉辦的「世界錄音帶日」（Cassette Store Day），也幫錄音帶銷售推了一把。世界錄音帶日在 2013 年由英國多個獨立唱片所發起，並聯合美國、德國、澳洲、紐西蘭等地的零售唱片行，舉辦一系列慶祝演唱、錄音帶獨家販售及促銷活動，參與陣容持續擴大中，也相對提高錄音帶能見度。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25175948/2017-01-24_174015.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F25175948%2F2017-01-24_174015.png&h=43bf53f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲ 世界錄音帶日 logo，還認得紅圓點和黑三角符號分別代表哪項錄音機功能嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n錄音帶與黑膠唱片的復甦儘管回不去過往榮景，仍能為許多人保存回憶中的樂曲溫度。好比《星際異攻隊》中，主角星爵熱愛懷舊樂曲是出於對母親的思念，即便身處在科技進步的時代，仍以卡式隨身聽收聽母親所錄製的卡帶歌曲，而這也是現今高科技所難以取代的情感連結。 <br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"http://technews.tw/2017/01/25/us-cassette-album-sales-increased-by-74-percent-in-2016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2Fus-cassette-album-sales-increased-by-74-percent-in-2016%2F&d=Pn1JixPKo7K482lIPxazvGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ba8848d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2017/01/25/us-cassette-album-sales-increased-by-74-percent-in-2016/</a>"},{"pid":"05f2141353ba2f6f0112c0773dd49b4eff43fcb3","tid":95073,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"証明蠢人多數鐘意扮野"},{"pid":"20dcdbf64bd0dea7b36034ccda0a98b9006376ff","tid":95073,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T21:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>証明蠢人多數鐘意扮野</blockquote><br />\n... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0795c101fdb093f54cbfaf42fa8e89129ae173db","tid":95073,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>証明蠢人多數鐘意扮野</blockquote><br />\n例如閣下"},{"pid":"8d21e7ece6bebd92ac402d70fe4f8ca3cd6aad8c","tid":95073,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>証明蠢人多數鐘意扮野</blockquote><br />\n例如閣下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b884cce5078327e6c5fdf333777fc8447437b8","tid":95073,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T23:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>証明蠢人多數鐘意扮野</blockquote><br />\n例如閣下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.